rComments: This prof was a ridiculous marker.. i actually took my papers to student appeals due to how unreasonable she marked my papers and was able to get a way higher grade because of doing so. Overall i felt she based her essay grades on who you were and not the quality of your paper since it was a small class she was able to pin point who was who.
pretty good overall - cant complain. midterm and finals are easy. hard marker for essays and tends to dock points for style mistakes. nice prof, easy to talk to, and generally knows her stuff.
